Dec 12 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Friday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

NOMURA HOLDINGS INC <8604.T> The Japanese financial services company said it appointed its co-deputy CFO Jonathan Lewis as CEO of the company's operations in Europe, Middle East and Africa. [ID:nL3N0TW33Y]  LLOYDS BANKING GROUP PLC <LLOY.L> The bank promoted Theresa Newell to the position of managing director and co-head of leveraged credit sales within its commercial banking business. [ID:nL6N0TW1FQ]  ROYAL BANK OF SCOTLAND GROUP PLC (RBS) <RBS.L>